## Store A Value [/storeavalue]

Sends a request to the Web service to store the given value under the given tag.

A Store A Value object has the following attributes:

+ STORED
+ tag
+ value - value to stored under the given tag.

### Store A Value Detail [POST]
+ Request (application/x-www-form-urlencoded)

        tag=1234567&value=abcdefg

+ Response 200 (application/json)


        [
            "STORED",
            "1434605731593",
            ""
        ]

